,{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"Crecimiento rapido en cultivo (1-3 dias)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"6","text":"Termofilicos → crecen bien a 37-42 grados C","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"6","text":"Ubicuos en ambiente → suelo, material organico en descomposicion","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Patogenesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Factores del\\Nhuesped","guid":"xjwQe9irykPJAKr9vb0xtA","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"HIERRO LIBRE\\NSERICO ELEVADO\\N→ factor critico","guid":"vHVTJKYdwWkDCzIrV1ekbQ","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Cetoacidosis diabetica → pH acido libera Fe de transferrina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Deferoxamina → sideroforo que Mucorales usa como xenosideroforo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Sobrecarga de hierro → talasemia, hemocromatosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"Neutropenia prolongada (RAN <500 por >=2 semanas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"23","text":"Inmunosupresion celular → TCMH, TOS, corticoides altos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"23","text":"Hiperglicemia → altera quimiotaxis de neutrofilos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"23","text":"COVID-19 → corticoides + hiperglicemia + linfopenia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"22","text":"Mecanismo\\Nde invasion","guid":"ZsH6N3fn-MEGMz-lkyiMMA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Receptor GRP78 endotelial → reconocido por CotH3 de Mucorales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Cascada EGFR → endocitosis del hongo por celula endotelial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"ANGIOINVASION →\\Ntrombosis vascular\\N→ necrosis tisular","guid":"qddccyxQUnh1apSK2twfZw","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Causa isquemia → dificulta penetracion de antifungicos","guid":"","c