o cubre)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Deferoxamina → contraindicada en sospecha","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"43","text":"Trauma/Quemaduras → mucormicosis cutanea en inmunocompetentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"43","text":"Desnutricion severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"43","text":"Uso de drogas IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"43","text":"GERIATRICO → DM + polifarmacia + inmunosenescencia + fragilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"Formas\\Nclinicas","guid":"KvoWKZ-7MW_IbB7R-tQMsg","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"RINOCEREBRAL\\N(rino-orbito-cerebral)\\N→ 30-50% casos","guid":"4wxKPKMhsLx963hk95QFGg","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Forma mas comun en DM/CAD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Progresion: sinusitis → orbita → SNC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"Sintomas\\Niniciales","guid":"L5WPUcdE9wRY5nqHvkPaEg","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Dolor facial/cefalea unilateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Congestion nasal con descarga sanguinolenta/oscura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"Fiebre (puede estar ausente en inmunosuprimidos)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"63","text":"Signos de\\Nalarma","guid":"26QLCvLzNctHhiUPavuqMg","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"ESCARA NEGRA en paladar o cornetes → patognomonico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Proptosis, oftalmoplegia → invasion orbitaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"Anestesia facial (V par)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"Alteracion conciencia → extension intracraneal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"63","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Trombosis de seno cavernoso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Invasion de arteria carotida interna","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"Absceso cerebral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"63","text":"MORTALIDAD 25-62% → hasta 80% con invasion SNC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"62","text":"PULMONAR →\\N15-30% casos","guid":"IJb2dCjzPR4FdWXQH6mM5A","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Forma mas comun en neutropenicos y TCMH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Presenta como neumonia rapidamente progresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"Hemoptisis → signo de alarma (angioinvasion)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"Imagenes\\NTC","guid":"UVpKZ5Sao8BKa5QAvX8qfQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Signo del HALO INVERSO → sugestivo (no patognomonico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Signo del Nido de Pajaro → estriaciones dentro de halo inverso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"Multiples nodulos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"Cavitaciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"Derrame pleural","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"84","text":"Sinusitis concomitante → aumenta sospecha","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"80","text":"MORTALIDAD 50-76%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"62","text":"CUTANEA →\\N10-15% casos","guid":"l54u_fDBoiT7ju9kYdRZkg","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Asociada a trauma, quemaduras, heridas quirurgicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"Puede verse en inmunocompetentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"Lesion necrotica progresiva → escara negra","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"MORTALIDAD menor (~15-30%) si solo cutanea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"62","text":"GASTROINT